00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:24.820
My father was a little
bit of a male chauvinist,

00:11:24.820 --> 00:11:26.620
and so that was
something I was like,

00:11:26.620 --> 00:11:30.432
I'm not going to try to change
your mind about that, other

00:11:30.432 --> 00:11:32.140
than I'm going to show
you what I can do.

00:11:32.140 --> 00:11:33.160
I'm going to show
you that I can do it.

00:11:33.160 --> 00:11:34.260
So I started boxing.

00:11:34.260 --> 00:11:36.275
And needless to say--

00:11:36.275 --> 00:11:37.400
maybe I do need to say it--

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:39.670
I did change his mind about it.

00:11:39.670 --> 00:11:42.790
Know He was like, wow,
