00:11:54.644 --> 00:11:57.520
and couldn't always be
there, but he was there.

00:11:57.520 --> 00:11:59.110
Over half of the
fights he was there.

00:11:59.110 --> 00:12:02.400
- So when he showed up, did
he try to sneak in the back?

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:04.160
- Oh my dad?

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:04.810
No.

00:12:04.810 --> 00:12:05.310
- Right.

00:12:08.980 --> 00:12:12.780
- Every time he walked in
it was like, Ali, Ali, Ali,

00:12:12.780 --> 00:12:13.630
and he loved it.

00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:16.005
- That's good for you because
the crowd was on your side.

00:12:16.005 --> 00:12:17.740
- Well yeah, but the crowd--

00:12:17.740 --> 00:12:21.304
was what was surreal about my
boxing career was just that I

00:12:21.304 --> 00:12:22.970
