00:21:47.180 --> 00:21:49.820
And so you know, there's
kind of like that old school

00:21:49.820 --> 00:21:51.470
feeling, right?

00:21:51.470 --> 00:21:54.920
But we also want to understand
that these women believe

00:21:54.920 --> 00:21:57.530
it's a sense of freedom,
even if us old people--

00:21:57.530 --> 00:22:00.350
not you, me-- would
go, wait a minute,

00:22:00.350 --> 00:22:02.660
