and you can be beautiful,

00:23:03.778 --> 00:23:06.430
and you can be powerful
with your clothes on.

00:23:06.430 --> 00:23:08.210
But some people
feel like they want

00:23:08.210 --> 00:23:10.210
to make a statement by
taking their clothes off.

00:23:10.210 --> 00:23:11.430
To each their own.

00:23:11.430 --> 00:23:15.010
But with the young
girls, I try to just--

00:23:15.010 --> 00:23:18.050
I think that if you love
yourself and you have

00:23:18.050 --> 00:23:21.560
confidence in yourself, and
you know what your values are,

00:23:21.560 --> 00:23:23.830
then it will be easier
to make those decisions

00:23:23.830 --> 00:23:25.271
when you're faced with them.

00:23:25.271 --> 00:23:27.020
Because there is going
to come a time when

00:23:27.020 --> 00:23:29.500
you're going to have to decide.

00:23:29.500 --> 00:23:31.250
- Right, and you think
