are with us probably forever.

00:24:00.154 --> 00:24:01.820
- And I didn't have
a problem with that.

00:24:01.820 --> 00:24:03.020
She just took off for shirt.

00:24:03.020 --> 00:24:04.311
She had sports braw underneath.

00:24:04.311 --> 00:24:05.330
It was just a moment.

00:24:05.330 --> 00:24:06.840
I don't think she really
thought that through.

00:24:06.840 --> 00:24:09.298
I'm going to take off my shirt
and show them how sexy I am.

00:24:09.298 --> 00:24:13.180
Lot of times male athletes
will take off their shirt,

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:13.840
