And you spent an
hour recording a PSA,

01:12:40.200 --> 01:12:42.616
and promoted on your social,
and the impact that that had.

01:12:42.616 --> 01:12:44.610
And would love to
hear from both of you

01:12:44.610 --> 01:12:47.190
for a minute in terms of what
you want your legacy to be.

01:12:47.190 --> 01:12:49.650
Both have mentioned
mentoring as something

01:12:49.650 --> 01:12:52.110
that's meaningful to you,
but when people look back

01:12:52.110 --> 01:12:54.900
on you in 20 or 30 or
40 years of your life--

01:12:54.900 --> 01:12:58.060
not your boxing life-- but your
personal life and your impact,

01:12:58.060 --> 01:13:01.410
what do you want your legacy
to be for both of you?

