About six now each year with
Northwestern, my alma mater,

01:13:21.690 --> 01:13:25.060
in Toledo, and with
the Association

01:13:25.060 --> 01:13:27.930
of Women in Sports Media, our
women's sports media group.

01:13:27.930 --> 01:13:30.870
It is very friendly with the
Women's Sports Foundation.

01:13:30.870 --> 01:13:34.710
And just helping young
people get into sports media,

01:13:34.710 --> 01:13:35.940
especially women.

01:13:35.940 --> 01:13:38.370
And we have thousands of
women now covering sports

01:13:38.370 --> 01:13:40.950
in this country, where we
only had a few when I started.

01:13:40.950 --> 01:13:44.370
So it's just hoping
that kids can

01:13:44.370 --> 01:13:47.160
reach their dreams, especially
young girls and women

01:13:47.160 --> 01:13:47.910
through sports.

01:13:47.910 --> 01:13:51.129
So that's among several
things, but that certainly

01:13:51.129 --> 01:13:52.170
is right up there for me.

01:13:52.170 --> 01:13:53.070
Thank you very much.

01:13:53.070 --> 01:13:55.020
And all you.

01:13:55.020 --> 01:13:55.979
Yes.

01:13:55.979 --> 01:13:56.520
- It's funny.

01:13:56.520 --> 01:14:01.100
I haven't really given that
question serious thought.

01:14:01.100 --> 01:14:03.374
You might have think I have.

01:14:03.374 --> 01:14:05.040
I feel like I'm right
in the thick of it

01:14:05.040 --> 01:14:09.210
right now, and still figuring
out a lot of things for myself

01:14:09.210 --> 01:14:14.100
and about myself, but I
can say that giving back

01:14:14.100 --> 01:14:15.990
is very important to me.

01:14:15.990 --> 01:14:18.270
Inspiring others
is important to me.

01:14:20.950 --> 01:14:25.030
I grew up in a very
dysfunctional family.

01:14:25.030 --> 01:14:26.510
A lot of people
don't realize that.

01:14:26.510 --> 01:14:29.570
When my parents got divorced,
my mom got remarried,

01:14:29.570 --> 01:14:31.750
and I went through a lot.

01:14:31.750 --> 01:14:35.680
And a lot of that is what turned
me into the fighter that I am.

01:14:35.680 --> 01:14:39.220
So I've learned a lot
about myself along the way.

01:14:39.220 --> 01:14:42.610
And I always try to
now just try to let

01:14:42.610 --> 01:14:45.540
others know that you never
can judge a book by its cover.

01:14:45.540 --> 01:14:48.091
We know that that saying,
and a lot of people

01:14:48.091 --> 01:14:50.590
would assume that I grew up
with a silver spoon in my mouth,

01:14:50.590 --> 01:14:51.800
and that wasn't the case.

01:14:51.800 --> 01:14:55.900
So I literally had
to fight from a kid,

01:14:55.900 --> 01:14:57.460
and I'm still fighting now.

01:14:57.460 --> 01:14:59.920
Now that I retired from
boxing, and I'm like, OK,

01:14:59.920 --> 01:15:01.210
I need to rebrand myself.

01:15:01.210 --> 01:15:03.335
I don't want to just be
the fighter because now I'm

01:15:03.335 --> 01:15:05.650
in this boxing box
of first it was like,

01:15:05.650 --> 01:15:08.200
I need to be taken seriously,
and now it's like, oh,

01:15:08.200 --> 01:15:10.840
I want to do TV and cross
over, and I have this fitness

01:15:10.840 --> 01:15:11.660
and wellness brand.

01:15:11.660 --> 01:15:13.660
And sometimes I can seem
intimidating to people,

01:15:13.660 --> 01:15:15.260
and I'm like wow.

01:15:15.260 --> 01:15:17.740
So it's really about
finding balance

01:15:17.740 --> 01:15:19.180
and I'm always fighting.

01:15:19.180 --> 01:15:22.570
But I just want to really
help as many other people

01:15:22.570 --> 01:15:26.410
as I can along the way while
still being true to myself.

01:15:26.410 --> 01:15:29.110
I don't think that there's
anything wrong with wanting

01:15:29.110 --> 01:15:31.060
certain things for yourself.

01:15:31.060 --> 01:15:35.420
And then figuring out what
God put me on earth for,

01:15:35.420 --> 01:15:38.740
make myself happy,
and do the work

01:15:38.740 --> 01:15:41.470
that I'm here to do, and bring
others along the way with me.

01:15:41.470 --> 01:15:43.720
So I'm never going to just
have all the clear answers.

01:15:43.720 --> 01:15:46.315
I'm still figuring things
out, but if I can help others

01:15:46.315 --> 01:15:48.940
with things that I do know, and
things that I have figured out,

01:15:48.940 --> 01:15:49.589
then great.

01:15:49.589 --> 01:15:51.130
But I never like to
come from a place

01:15:51.130 --> 01:15:52.630
like, oh, I got it
all figured out.

01:15:52.630 --> 01:15:55.000
I'm going to be 40
years old soon--

01:15:55.000 --> 01:15:56.960
December 30.

01:15:56.960 --> 01:15:58.120
- Kid you.

01:15:58.120 --> 01:16:00.700
- I'm excited about it.

01:16:00.700 --> 01:16:02.287
A lot of people are like--

01:16:02.287 --> 01:16:04.120
they worry about getting
older, but I'm just

01:16:04.120 --> 01:16:05.980
happy to be healthy,
and have a family,

01:16:05.980 --> 01:16:09.550
and have so many different
opportunities before me.

01:16:09.550 --> 01:16:12.820
And I really do feel like I can
do anything that I want to do,

01:16:12.820 --> 01:16:15.220
it's just a matter of
deciding what I want to do.

01:16:15.220 --> 01:16:17.130
And I'm really blessed--

01:16:17.130 --> 01:16:19.480
I know to even just have
that kind of confidence,

01:16:19.480 --> 01:16:21.610
and I know that it came
through my parents.

01:16:21.610 --> 01:16:23.630
And it came from
them by example.

01:16:23.630 --> 01:16:25.870
My dad didn't sit down and
have conversations with me

01:16:25.870 --> 01:16:28.720
about how to be confident,
how to believe in myself.

01:16:28.720 --> 01:16:30.100
He just believed in himself.

01:16:30.100 --> 01:16:31.390
He was confident in himself.

01:16:31.390 --> 01:16:33.822
And the language that we
speak-- the way we speak about

01:16:33.822 --> 01:16:35.530
ourselves, the way we
speak about others,

01:16:35.530 --> 01:16:38.020
the conversations that we
have in our household--

01:16:38.020 --> 01:16:39.670
kids learn from watching.

01:16:39.670 --> 01:16:41.680
So for me, I want to
be there for my kids.

01:16:41.680 --> 01:16:44.560
And I want to be that for
anybody else watching me.

01:16:44.560 --> 01:16:47.830
Something that I say today
might spark something

01:16:47.830 --> 01:16:49.750
in an individual and
change their life.

01:16:49.750 --> 01:16:51.760
So that's all.

01:16:51.760 --> 01:16:54.220
don't I can't say--

01:16:54.220 --> 01:16:57.940
I don't have a two sentence
answer for that, but whatever

01:16:57.940 --> 01:17:00.430
you can take from that.

01:17:00.430 --> 01:17:00.970
That's it.

01:17:00.970 --> 01:17:02.110
That's all I can say.

01:17:02.110 --> 01:17:03.610
- How great.

01:17:03.610 --> 01:17:05.110
- I hate to end that way.

01:17:05.110 --> 01:17:06.610
- That was fantastic.

01:17:06.610 --> 01:17:07.810
That was good.

01:17:07.810 --> 01:17:09.360
- Thanks.

